Revision history for Perl extension HTML::Template::HashWrapper.

1.3   7 Jan 2003
      No functional changes.
      Tests will now run fine even if Test::Exception is not installed.

1.2   6 Jan 2004
      Horrible realization that the idea behind HashWrapper::Plain was
      fatally flawed.  Redone with more realistic expectations.

1.1   23 Dec 2003
      Allow for more flexible subclassing 
      (based on a suggestion by Timm Murray).

1.0   21 Dec 2003
      First public release.

0.01  Sun Dec 21 13:08:29 2003
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.22 with options
		-n HashWrapper -O -P -X -A

